model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder

Class AStarPathFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder.PathFinder
      • model.agent.humanAgent.tacticalLevel.navigation.pathfinder.AStarPathFinder

  • public class AStarPathFinder
extends PathFinder
    The A* Path Finder uses the A* algorithm to find a path from a start Position to a goal Position. Returns a path with only the goal position if no path could be found.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen

        private double getHeuristicDistance(AStarNode node,
                                    AStarNode goal)
        Gets the heuristic distance between two AStarNodes. It is the euclidean distance between the two nodes (while assuming no obstacles), but corrects for the maximum angle allowed in the graph.
        Parameters:
        node - The starting node.
        goal - The goal node.
        Returns:
        The heuristic distance between the nodes.
